title: Paco de Lucia - Concierto de Aranjuez [FLAC] TQMP
description:
Paco de Lucia - Concierto de Aranjuez
1991

Brought to you by TQMP
The Quality Music Project

Joaquin Rodrigo's Concierto de Aranjuez
Conductor: Edmon Colomer
Orchestra: Orquesta de Cadaques
Guitar: Paco de Lucia

Issac Albeniz' Iberia
Paco de Lucia
Jose M. Bandera
Juan Manuel Canizares

This concert was part of a series of cultural events to celebrate the 500 Centenary of the discovery of the New World (in Spanish "discovery" is a synonym for invasion, massacre, bloodshed and pillage. Yes, our language is THAT rich. LOL). Joaquin Rodrigo's concert is a very nice piece of work and Paco delivers as usual. I find his rendition faster than other versions. No surprise here. All in all a great concert. A must have for Paco fans or Aranjuez maniacs.

Tracks
01- Concierto de Aranjuez - Allegro Con Spirito
02- Concierto de Aranjuez - Adagio
03- Concierto de Aranjuez - Allegro Gentile
04- Iberia - Triana
05- Iberia - El Albaicin
06- Iberia - El Puerto
